      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="content has-text-centered">
      <h1 class="title is-2 is-white is-bold">
        Don't just own domains. Invest in them.
      </h1>
      <p class="subtitle is-4 is-whitelight">
        Sell more domains with powerful and streamlined professional tools.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <form id="tryit-form" action="/compare?domain_name=">
