            </div>
            <span>Sign Up Free</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div id="foo" class="content has-text-centered">
      <p class="is-whitelight">
        It only takes minutes to set up!
      </p>
      <figure class="image is-24x24">
